scripts.start_psql: docker run -d -p 5432:5432 --workdir /app --name ui-test_postgres_1 -e POSTGRES_USER='ui_test' -e POSTGRES_DB='ui_test' -e POSTGRES_PASSWORD=password postgres:14.1-alpine && docker cp models ui-test_postgres_1:/app
scripts.create_users: docker exec -ti ui-test_postgres_1 psql -U ui_test -d ui_test -w password -f /app/models/users.sql
